'From Squeak3.1alpha of 5 February 2001 [latest update: #4227] on 1 August 2001 at 3:08:54 pm'!"Change Set:		TextMorphTweakDate:			1 August 2001Author:			Dan IngallsThe first time you bring up the Text's menu from the red handle, AutoFit was not checked even thought AutoFit is on.  Now it works correctly."!!TextMorph methodsFor: 'menu' stamp: 'di 8/1/2001 14:32'!autoFitString	"Answer the string to put in a menu that will invite the user to switch autoFit mode"	^ (self isAutoFit		ifTrue: ['<yes>']		ifFalse: ['<no>'])		, 'text auto fit'! !